trans-unit.source: Represents a proposed removal of an <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity" /> from a <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity" /> within a running workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Representa una eliminación propuesta de un <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity" /> de un <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity" /> dentro de una instancia de flujo de trabajo en ejecución.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.RemovedActivityAction" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.RemovedActivityAction" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.RemovedActivityAction" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.RemovedActivityAction" />.

trans-unit.source: Indicates the index of the activity being removed when you remove the activity using the workflow changes.
trans-unit.target: Indica el índice de la actividad quitada al quitar la actividad mediante los cambios del flujo de trabajo.

trans-unit.source: Root activity from which the activity was removed.
trans-unit.target: Actividad raíz de la que se quitó la actividad.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.RemovedActivityAction" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.RemovedActivityAction" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the instance of original <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity" /> being removed.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene la instancia de <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity" /> original quitado.

trans-unit.source: The instance of the original <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity" /> being removed.

Gets index of the removed <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity" /> with the <see cref="P:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity.Activities" /> collection of the parent <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene índice del <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity" /> agregado con la colección <see cref="P:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity.Activities" /> del <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity" />primario.

trans-unit.source: The index of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity" /> being removed.
trans-unit.target: Índice de <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity" /> que se va a quitar.
